@NODE "installation" "Installation"
@TOC "MAIN"

 INSTALLATION

   1. Put the SnakesFW catalog anywhere you like on your Harddrive.

   2. Copy the Microknight font to your FONTS: directory. Without it
      the game won't run.

   3. Click on the Snakes icon to start the game.

  That's it. Have fun!

@ENDNODE

